<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Payout Confirmed - TamWill</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000000;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 2px solid #000000;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #000000; 
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 0 10px;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .project-info {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border: 2px solid #000000;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .amount-box {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border: 2px solid #000000;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .status-success {
            color: #059669;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">TamWill</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Payout Confirmed</h2>

            <p><strong>Hello {{ project.creator.name }},</strong></p>

            <p>Great news! Your payout request for project <strong>{{ project.title }}</strong> has been confirmed and processed.</p>

            <div class="project-info">
                <strong>Project:</strong> {{ project.title }}<br>
                <strong>Amount:</strong> {{ project.collectedAmount }}â‚¬<br>
                <strong>RIB:</strong> {{ project.rib }}<br>
                <strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-success">Confirmed</span>
            </div>

            <div class="amount-box">
                {{ project.collectedAmount }}â‚¬ Bank Transfer Initiated
            </div>

            <p><strong>What happens next:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>The bank transfer will be processed within 2-3 business days</li>
                <li>You will receive the funds directly to your registered bank account</li>
                <li>You will receive a separate confirmation from your bank once the transfer is complete</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="warning">
                <strong>ðŸ“§ IMPORTANT:</strong> Keep this email as confirmation of your payout approval. If you have any questions or don't receive the transfer within 5 business days, please contact our support team.
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">
                Thank you for using TamWill to fund your project. We're glad we could help you achieve your funding goals!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Sent to {{ project.creator.email }}</p>
            <p>Project ID: {{ project.id }} | Processed on {{ 'now'|date('F j, Y \\a\\t g:i A') }}</p>
            <p>&copy; {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} TamWill Inc.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
